column2: Baggit Unisex Brown Fighter Bindas Travel Wallet
column19:
• Product Description
  • Style Note

  • Set a style statement with this sleek leather travel wallet from Baggit. This piece epitomises class. We recommend that you invest in this accessory to keep you monetary essentials in order.

  • Product Details

  • Brown coloured two fold travel wallet
column20:
has stitched detail and cut out detail at the front
The right flap has one slip pocket with five holders to organize passport and other documents
The left flap has one slip pocket with a zipped separator sleeve along with eleven card holders and an ID card holder
An external zipped pocket with branding at the back
Water resistant lining
Warranty: 9 months

  • Material & Care

  • Synthetic leather
    Wipe with a clean
column21:
dry cloth when needed
